### Variables de entorno del archivo .http
@host = http://localhost:8080

# =====================================================================
#  Este archivo documenta el CONSUMO de la API por módulo.
#  Se irá ampliando a medida que se construye cada módulo.
#  Ejecutable desde VS Code (REST Client) o JetBrains Rider.
# =====================================================================

### [Disponible] Home / landing
GET {{host}}/
Accept: text/html

# =====================================================================
#  AUTH / IDENTITY  (cookies + Identity)
# =====================================================================

### Registrar HUÉSPED (rol Guest por defecto) -> 200 + set-cookie
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "huesped@demo.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!",
  "firstName": "Ana",
  "lastName": "García"
}

### Registrar PROPIETARIO (rol Owner) -> 200 + set-cookie
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dueno@demo.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!",
  "firstName": "Carlos",
  "lastName": "Pérez",
  "role": "Owner"
}

### Login -> 200 + set-cookie (.AspNetCore.Identity.Application)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "huesped@demo.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!",
  "rememberMe": true
}

### Usuario actual (requiere cookie) -> 200 con AuthUserDto / 401
GET {{host}}/api/auth/me

### Logout (requiere cookie) -> 204
POST {{host}}/api/auth/logout

# =====================================================================
#  PROPIEDADES  (catálogo público anónimo + gestión del dueño)
# =====================================================================

### Buscar catálogo (anónimo) con filtros de ciudad + disponibilidad
GET {{host}}/api/properties?city=Bogota&checkIn=2026-07-01&checkOut=2026-07-05&minGuests=2&page=1&pageSize=12

### Detalle de inmueble (anónimo, cacheado en Redis)
GET {{host}}/api/properties/1

### [Owner] Publicar inmueble (requiere cookie de un usuario Owner)
POST {{host}}/api/properties
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Apartamento con vista",
  "description": "Acogedor, cerca de todo.",
  "city": "Bogota",
  "country": "Colombia",
  "addressLine": "Calle 100 #15-20",
  "pricePerNight": 250000,
  "maxGuests": 4,
  "bedrooms": 2,
  "bathrooms": 1
}

### [Owner] Editar inmueble
PUT {{host}}/api/properties/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Apartamento con vista (actualizado)",
  "description": "Renovado.",
  "city": "Bogota",
  "country": "Colombia",
  "pricePerNight": 280000,
  "maxGuests": 4,
  "bedrooms": 2,
  "bathrooms": 2
}

### [Owner] Mis inmuebles
GET {{host}}/api/properties/mine

### [Owner] Subir imagen (multipart -> MinIO bucket público)
POST {{host}}/api/properties/1/images
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isCover"

true
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="foto.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./foto.jpg
------Boundary--

### [Owner] Desactivar inmueble
DELETE {{host}}/api/properties/1

# =====================================================================
#  NOTIFICACIONES  (in-app; el correo se ve en MailHog http://localhost:8025)
# =====================================================================

### Mis notificaciones (?unreadOnly=true para solo no leídas)
GET {{host}}/api/notifications

### Conteo de no leídas (badge)
GET {{host}}/api/notifications/unread-count

### Marcar una como leída -> 204
POST {{host}}/api/notifications/1/read

### Marcar todas como leídas -> 204
POST {{host}}/api/notifications/read-all

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
#  Módulos planeados (endpoints en construcción):
#
# =====================================================================
#  FAVORITOS / WISHLIST  (requiere sesión; idempotente)
# =====================================================================

### Mi wishlist
GET {{host}}/api/favorites

### Agregar a favoritos -> 204
POST {{host}}/api/favorites/1

### Quitar de favoritos -> 204
DELETE {{host}}/api/favorites/1
#
# =====================================================================
#  RESERVAS  (requiere sesión + KYC aprobado)
# =====================================================================

### Crear reserva -> 201 (horas 14:00/12:00 fijadas por el sistema)
POST {{host}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "propertyId": 1,
  "checkInDate": "2026-07-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-07-05"
}

### Mis reservas (incluye CheckInDateTime/CheckOutDateTime estándar)
GET {{host}}/api/bookings/mine

### Detalle de reserva
GET {{host}}/api/bookings/1

### Cancelar reserva -> 204 (libera fechas)
POST {{host}}/api/bookings/1/cancel
#
# =====================================================================
#  KYC  (validación de identidad: OCR + cifrado + veredicto)
# =====================================================================

### Subir cédula (multipart) -> veredicto Approved/Rejected
POST {{host}}/api/kyc/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="cedula.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./cedula.jpg
------Boundary--

### Estado de mi KYC
GET {{host}}/api/kyc/status

# =====================================================================
#  DASHBOARD + REPORTES  (rol Owner)
# =====================================================================

### Dashboard (por defecto últimos 30 días)
GET {{host}}/api/owner/dashboard

### Dashboard con periodo y filtro por inmueble
GET {{host}}/api/owner/dashboard?from=2026-06-01&to=2026-06-30&propertyId=1

### Descargar reporte Excel (.xlsx) de todo el portafolio
GET {{host}}/api/owner/reports/excel?from=2026-06-01&to=2026-06-30

### Reporte Excel filtrado por inmueble
GET {{host}}/api/owner/reports/excel?propertyId=1
